snippet.title: [Brutal Universe] February gamejam [Spinning]
snippet.description:
Hey, this is our entry to the gamejam. We hope you enjoy the trailer and feel free to try the game.

Download the game here Windows/Mac:  https://arvid-nygren.itch.io/brutal-universe

Credits:

Game Development

Arvid Nygren http://arvidnygren.com/
Noah Hjerdin https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMkTBq01UgF7_pu10pfZBTA?view_as=subscriber

Music and video

Albin Lindh  (Instagram: Albinjo02)
Me (Skal1)

Thank you!
